# Why Brute Force is Slow?

Suppose

```
n = 1000

length = 1000
```

For every word

```
1000 prefixes
```

Each prefix compares with

```
1000 words
```

Each `startswith()` may compare up to

```
1000 characters
```

Very expensive.

